More information and reason for this action is here: https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_Program_Management/HouseKeeping/Fedora24#Rawhide_Rebase

Created attachment 1136835 Patch to fix the FTBFS
The FTBFS is primarily caused by doc installation inconsistencies.
I am proposing the patch in the attachment (againt fedora git/master), which is supposed to clean up these and other minor issues (mostly rpm anachronisms).
Unless somebody objects, I will apply this patch to rawhide and f24 in near future.
